data.description: Country setting in an established neighborhood sitting on over an acre of land.  This 2 story home with 4 bedrooms and 3 baths could be the one you and your family have been searching for. The master suite features a huge closet and an additional office room. The living room boasts with wood details around the wood fireplace and beamed ceilings. The Kitchen is open to dining area and overlooks back patio. Upstairs offers so much space with extra large bedrooms with adequate closets, 3rd bath and large game room. Schedule your personal showing today before it gets away!This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee). See the attached Vendee form for more details.
